dct_title_s: Map of the rail-roads of the state of New York prepared under the direction of the Rail Road Commissioners, John S. Clark, William J. McAlpine, James B. Swain
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Shows railroads in operation, in progress of construction, and proposed. Also shows canals. Princeton copy 2: Imperfect, portion at left lacking. [Railroad Commission]. Relief shown by hachures. Different colors indicate railroads in operation, in progress of construction and proposed; canals are located.. Lith. Of C. Van Benthuysen.
dct_publisher_sm: Albany, New York : C. Van Benthuysen, 1856.
